<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Secure Verification - PH Health Management</title>
    <style>
        /* Email Reset */
        body, table, td, a { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; }
        body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background-color: #0f172a; }
        
        /* Outer Canvas (Dark Mode Vibe) */
        .email-canvas {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #0f172a; /* Deep Slate */
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, #1e293b 0%, #0f172a 80%);
            padding: 60px 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* The Main Floating Card */
        .premium-card {
            max-width: 540px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        /* Brand Header */
        .card-header {
            padding: 40px 40px 20px 40px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .brand-name {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #0f172a;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #e0f2fe;
            color: #0284c7;
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.2px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        /* Content Area */
        .card-body {
            padding: 0 40px 30px 40px;
        }
        .greeting-text {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #334155;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .highlight-name {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        /* The Dark OTP Compartment */
        .otp-display-unit {
            background-color: #0f172a;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 35px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #1e293b;
            box-shadow: inset 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .otp-eyebrow {
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: block;
        }
        .otp-code {
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            font-size: 52px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #38bdf8; /* Bright Cyan/Blue */
            letter-spacing: 18px;
            margin: 0;
            margin-right: -18px; /* Fix offset from letter-spacing */
            text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.3); /* Subtle glow effect */
        }

        /* Meta Data Table */
        .meta-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .meta-table td {
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .meta-table td:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .meta-label {
            color: #64748b;
            font-weight: 500;
            width: 40%;
        }
        .meta-value {
            color: #0f172a;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: right;
        }
        .status-dot {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            background-color: #10b981;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 6px;
        }

        /* Inner Footer / Security */
        .security-banner {
            background-color: #fff1f2;
            border-left: 4px solid #e11d48;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #9f1239;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* Outer Footer (Outside the card) */
        .email-footer {
            max-width: 540px;
            margin: 30px auto 0;
            text-align: center;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 12px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .email-footer a {
            color: #94a3b8;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-canvas">
        
        <div class="premium-card">
            
            <div class="card-header">
                <div>
                    <h1 class="brand-name">PH Health</h1>
                    <div class="badge">Authorization Required</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="greeting-text">
                    Hello <span class="highlight-name"><%= name %></span>,<br><br>
                    A request has been made to securely access your PH Health Management dashboard. Enter the code below to verify your identity.
                </div>

                <div class="otp-display-unit">
                    <span class="otp-eyebrow">Secure Access Code</span>
                    <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
                </div>

                <table class="meta-table">
                    <tr>
                        <td class="meta-label">Validity Period</td>
                        <td class="meta-value">2 Minutes</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="meta-label">Connection</td>
                        <td class="meta-value"><span class="status-dot"></span> Secure (TLS)</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>

                <div class="security-banner">
                    <strong>Do not share this code.</strong> Our medical and support staff will never ask you for this password over the phone or via email.
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>

        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> PH Health Management Systems. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>If you did not initiate this request, your account is safe, but you may want to <a href="#">review your security settings</a>.</p>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>
</html>